title: Can someone id this typeface?
content:
[http://www.eureka.com/](http://web.archive.org/web/20081021110830/http:/www.eureka.com/ "http://www.eureka.com/")

I really like the typeface up in the top corner used for the buttons. Can someone please ID the type family for me please.  
Thank you.

author: nha Tran

comments.content: I can’t ID the font directly, but you may be able to find something you like here: [http://www.dafont.com/bitmap.php](http://web.archive.org/web/20081021110830/http:/www.dafont.com/bitmap.php "http://www.dafont.com/bitmap.php")

If you are looking for a nice pixel font, look no further then the free [Unibody](http://web.archive.org/web/20081021110830/http:/www.underware.nl/site2/index.php?id1=unibody&id2=overview) from Underware.
